title: Shiny Toy Guns- Rarities and Bsides
description:
Rarities I collected from the web or got through other means. Enjoy.

I'm pretty sure NONE of these tracks are available for download anywhere else. A few might be. I feel it necessary to say that I didn't include certain things (Ricochet Remixes, Rainy Monday remixes) as they are widely available.


Any tracks labeled "Pre-Version" feature the band's first female singer, Ursula Vari. They were never released on We Are Pilots.
